OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fprobably become increasing confined to
OL,7,Fsouthernmost areas during this
OL,8,Fevening, with drier, though still
OL,9,Frather cloudy weather elsewhere. Rain
OL,10,Fand drizzle returning northwards at
OL,11,Ftimes overnight. Winds becoming light.
OL,12,FCooler than last night, but frost free.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FSouthern areas will often be
OL,15,Fwet with rain at times. Further north
OL,16,Fit looks mostly dry, with brighter
OL,17,Fbreaks. Mild with light winds, though
OL,18,Ffeeling cooler in any rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
