OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FOvernight rain, perhaps with some hill
OL,7,Fsnow, giving way to brighter skies on
OL,8,FSaturday. Turning damp and windy on
OL,9,FSunday. Brighter, but still showery
OL,10,Fand breezy on Monday. Staying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
